#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:2
msgid "Registering an Object Type"
msgstr "注册对象类型"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:5
msgid "Registering a Reference Type"
msgstr "注册引用类型"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:7
msgid ""
"The basic reference type will be instantiated by factory function and "
"managed by reference counting."
msgstr ""
"基本引用类型将通过工厂函数实例化，并由引用计数管理。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:9
msgid ""
"Unlike the value type, the underlying C++ type for reference type can be "
"incomplete type. This is designed to support the common C API pattern, "
"which typically consists of an opaque structure pointer and a set of C "
"functions."
msgstr ""
"与值类型不同，引用类型的底层 C++ 类型可以是不完整类型。"
"这是为了支持常见的 C API 模式而设计的，"
"该模式通常由一个不透明结构指针和一组 C 函数组成。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:14
msgid "Factory"
msgstr "工厂"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:17
msgid "Factory Functions"
msgstr "工厂函数"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:19
msgid ""
"Factory functions can be automatically generated from constructors of C++"
" type. The memory for new object will be allocated using ``new``, so if "
"an allocation function provided by user is required, you can create a "
"custom overload of ``operator new``."
msgstr ""
"工厂函数可以从 C++ 类型的构造函数自动生成。"
"新对象的内存将使用 ``new`` 分配，因此如果需要用户提供的分配函数，"
"可以创建 ``operator new`` 的自定义重载。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:23
msgid ""
"If you already have a function for instantiating the class, you can "
"register it by ``.factory_function``."
msgstr ""
"如果你已经有一个用于实例化类的函数，可以通过 ``.factory_function`` 注册它。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:39
msgid ""
"You need to provide a parameter list for factories other than the default"
" factory."
msgstr ""
"除默认工厂外，你需要为其他工厂提供参数列表。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:49 ../../doc/object_type.rst:271
msgid ""
"If you want certain factories to be marked with ``explicit``, you can use"
" the tag ``use_explicit``. Just put the tag right after the parameter "
"list."
msgstr ""
"如果你希望某些工厂标记为 ``explicit``，可以使用标签 ``use_explicit``。"
"只需将标签放在参数列表后面即可。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:59
msgid "Factory with Auxiliary Object"
msgstr "带辅助对象的工厂"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:61
msgid "It might be useful to call the factory with a helper object."
msgstr "使用辅助对象调用工厂可能会很有用。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:85
msgid ""
"If the factory function with an auxiliary object is not a member "
"function, the parameter for receiving pointer to auxiliary object will be"
" located by the following logic:"
msgstr ""
"如果带辅助对象的工厂函数不是成员函数，"
"接收辅助对象指针的参数将按以下逻辑定位："

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:88
msgid ""
"Check if the first/last parameter is a reference/pointer to the helper "
"object"
msgstr ""
"检查第一个/最后一个参数是否为辅助对象的引用/指针"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:89 ../../doc/object_type.rst:285
#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:412
msgid ""
"If both first and last parameters satisfy the condition, asbind20 will "
"prefer the first one."
msgstr ""
"如果第一个和最后一个参数都满足条件，asbind20 将优先选择第一个。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:91 ../../doc/object_type.rst:287
#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:417
msgid ""
"If this is not the desired behaviour, you can manually specify the "
"position of that special parameter."
msgstr ""
"如果这不是期望的行为，你可以手动指定该特殊参数的位置。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:100
msgid ""
"Specially, the auxiliary object can be the ``asITypeInfo*`` of type being"
" registered. This can be done by the tag ``this_type``."
msgstr ""
"特别地，辅助对象可以是正在注册的类型的 ``asITypeInfo*``。"
"这可以通过标签 ``this_type`` 实现。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:103
msgid "This might be helpful when dealing with garbage collected types."
msgstr "这在处理垃圾回收类型时可能会很有帮助。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:117
msgid "List Factory"
msgstr "列表工厂"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:119
msgid ""
"List factory allows the reference type to be created from an "
"initialization list."
msgstr ""
"列表工厂允许从初始化列表创建引用类型。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:121 ../../doc/object_type.rst:300
msgid ":doc:`It will be discussed in a separate page. <advanced/init_list>`"
msgstr ":doc:`它将在单独的页面中讨论。 <advanced/init_list>`"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:124
msgid "Behaviours for Reference Counting"
msgstr "引用计数的行为"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:126
msgid "The basic reference type uses reference counting to manage its lifetime."
msgstr "基本引用类型使用引用计数来管理其生命周期。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:155
msgid "Tips for Reference Types"
msgstr "引用类型提示"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:157
msgid ""
"For reference counted type, the reference counter should be set to ``1`` "
"during initialization."
msgstr ""
"对于引用计数类型，引用计数器应在初始化时设置为 ``1``。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:159
msgid ""
"If your type involves GC, you need to notify the GC of a newly "
"instantiated object by ``NotifyGarbageCollectorOfNewObject``, `as "
"explained in AngelScript's official document "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_gc_object.html#doc_reg_gcref_2>`_."
msgstr ""
"如果你的类型涉及 GC，你需要通过 ``NotifyGarbageCollectorOfNewObject`` 通知 GC 新实例化的对象，"
"`如 AngelScript 官方文档所述 "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_gc_object.html#doc_reg_gcref_2>`_。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:162
msgid ""
"asbind20 also provides a policy called ``policies::notify_gc`` for (list)"
" factory functions to automatically notify the GC after a new object is "
"created."
msgstr ""
"asbind20 还提供了一个名为 ``policies::notify_gc`` 的策略，用于（列表）工厂函数在创建新对象后自动通知 GC。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:165
msgid "Registering a Value Type"
msgstr "注册值类型"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:167
msgid ""
"The underlying C++ type for value type must be a complete type, i.e., "
"``sizeof(T)`` is a valid expression."
msgstr ""
"值类型的底层 C++ 类型必须是完整类型，即 ``sizeof(T)`` 是一个有效的表达式。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:171
msgid "Flags of Value Type"
msgstr "值类型的标志"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:173
msgid ""
"If the type doesn't require any special treatment, i.e. doesn't contain "
"any pointers or other resource references that must be maintained, then "
"the type can be registered with the flag ``asOBJ_POD``. In this case "
"AngelScript doesn't require the default constructor, assignment "
"behaviour, or destructor, as it will be able to automatically handle "
"these cases the same way it handles built-in primitives."
msgstr ""
"如果类型不需要任何特殊处理，即不包含任何必须维护的指针或其他资源引用，"
"那么该类型可以使用标志 ``asOBJ_POD`` 注册。在这种情况下，"
"AngelScript 不需要默认构造函数、赋值行为或析构函数，"
"因为它能够像处理内置基本类型一样自动处理这些情况。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:179
msgid ""
"If you plan on passing or returning the type by value to registered "
"functions that uses native calling convention, you also need to inform "
"how the type is implemented in the application. But if you only plan on "
":doc:`using generic calling conventions <advanced/generic>`, or don't "
"pass these types by value then you don't need to worry about that."
msgstr ""
"如果你计划将类型按值传递给使用原生调用约定的注册函数，"
"你还需要告知类型在应用程序中的实现方式。"
"但如果你只计划 :doc:`使用通用调用约定 <advanced/generic>`，或不按值传递这些类型，则无需担心这一点。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:184
msgid ""
"The asbind20 will handle common flags for you. However, due to limitation"
" of C++, the following flags still need user to provide them manually."
msgstr ""
"asbind20 将为你处理常见标志。然而，由于 C++ 的限制，"
"以下标志仍需要用户手动提供。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:191
msgid "Flag"
msgstr "标志"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:192
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:194
msgid "``asOBJ_APP_CLASS_MORE_CONSTRUCTORS``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:195
msgid ""
"The C++ class has additional constructors beyond the default/copy "
"constructor"
msgstr ""
"C++ 类具有除默认/拷贝构造函数之外的其他构造函数"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:197
msgid "``asOBJ_APP_CLASS_ALLINTS``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:198
msgid "The C++ class members can be treated as if all integers"
msgstr "C++ 类成员可以视为都是整数类型"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:200
msgid "``asOBJ_APP_CLASS_ALLFLOATS``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:201
msgid ""
"The C++ class members can be treated as if all ``float``\\ s or "
"``double``\\ s"
msgstr ""
"C++ 类成员可以视为都是 ``float`` 或 ``double`` 类型"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:203
msgid "``asOBJ_APP_CLASS_ALIGN8``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:204
msgid "The C++ class contains members that may require 8-byte alignment."
msgstr "C++ 类包含可能需要 8 字节对齐的成员。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:206
msgid "For example, a ``double``"
msgstr "例如，一个 ``double``"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:208
msgid "``asOBJ_APP_CLASS_UNION``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:209
msgid "The C++ class contains unions as members"
msgstr "C++ 类包含联合体作为成员"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:212
msgid ""
"C++ compiler may provide some functions automatically if one of the "
"members is of a type that requires it. So even if the type you want to "
"register doesn't have a declared default constructor, it may still be "
"necessary to register the type with the flag "
"``asOBJ_APP_CLASS_MORE_CONSTRUCTORS``."
msgstr ""
"如果某个成员是需要构造函数的类型，C++ 编译器可能会自动提供一些函数。"
"因此，即使你想要注册的类型没有声明的默认构造函数，"
"仍然可能需要使用标志 ``asOBJ_APP_CLASS_MORE_CONSTRUCTORS`` 注册该类型。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:217
msgid ""
"Be careful to inform the correct flags, because if the wrong flags are "
"used you may get unexpected behaviour when calling registered functions "
"that receives or returns these types by value. Common problems are stack "
"corruptions or invalid memory accesses. In some cases you may face more "
"silent errors that may be difficult to detect, e.g., the function is not "
"returning the expected values."
msgstr ""
"请小心提供正确的标志，因为如果使用了错误的标志，"
"在调用按值接收或返回这些类型的注册函数时可能会出现意外行为。"
"常见问题包括栈损坏或无效内存访问。在某些情况下，"
"你可能会遇到更难以检测的静默错误，例如函数未返回预期的值。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:223
msgid ""
"You can also read the official documentation about `value types and "
"native calling conventions "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_register_val_type.html#doc_reg_val_2>`_"
" ."
msgstr ""
"你也可以阅读关于 `值类型和原生调用约定 "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_register_val_type.html#doc_reg_val_2>`_ 的官方文档。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:227
msgid "Constructors and Destructor"
msgstr "构造函数和析构函数"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:230
msgid "Constructor Functions"
msgstr "构造函数"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:232
msgid ""
"The memory of value types are allocated by AngelScript, then the memory "
"needs to be initialized using the placement ``new``."
msgstr ""
"值类型的内存由 AngelScript 分配，然后需要使用 placement ``new`` 进行初始化。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:235
msgid ""
"If you already have a function for initializing the class, you can "
"register it by ``.constructor_function``. You can also use a lambda to "
"create a constructor function in-place."
msgstr ""
"如果你已经有一个用于初始化类的函数，可以通过 ``.constructor_function`` 注册它。"
"你也可以使用 lambda 原地创建构造函数。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:253
msgid ""
"You need to provide a parameter list for constructors other than the "
"default/copy constructor."
msgstr ""
"除默认/拷贝构造函数外，你需要为其他构造函数提供参数列表。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:281
msgid ""
"The parameter for receiving pointer to allocated memory will be located "
"by the following logic:"
msgstr ""
"接收分配内存指针的参数将按以下逻辑定位："

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:283
msgid ""
"Check if the first/last parameter is a reference/pointer to the type "
"being registered"
msgstr ""
"检查第一个/最后一个参数是否为正在注册的类型的引用/指针"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:284
msgid "Check if the type of first/last parameter is ``void*``"
msgstr "检查第一个/最后一个参数的类型是否为 ``void*``"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:296
msgid "List Constructor"
msgstr "列表构造函数"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:298
msgid ""
"The list constructor allows the value type to be initialized from an "
"initialization list."
msgstr ""
"列表构造函数允许从初始化列表初始化值类型。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:303
msgid "Destructor"
msgstr "析构函数"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:311
msgid "Automatically Registering Required Behaviours"
msgstr "自动注册所需的行为"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:313
msgid ""
"You can call the ``.behaviours_by_traits()`` to automatically register "
"type behaviours required by the type flags. It will register default "
"constructor, copy constructor, destructor, and assignment operator "
"(``operator=``/``opAssign``) according to the type flags."
msgstr ""
"你可以调用 ``.behaviours_by_traits()`` 来自动注册类型标志所需的行为。"
"它将根据类型标志注册默认构造函数、拷贝构造函数、析构函数和赋值运算符"
"（``operator=``/``opAssign``）。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:318
msgid ""
"Be careful not to register those behaviours again by standalone helpers, "
"otherwise you will get an error message about duplicated things."
msgstr ""
"注意不要通过独立的辅助函数再次注册这些行为，否则你会收到关于重复内容的错误信息。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:321
msgid ""
"This helper function uses flags provided by ``asGetTypeTraits<T>()`` by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"该辅助函数默认使用 ``asGetTypeTraits<T>()`` 提供的标志。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:328
msgid "You can also provide the flags manually:"
msgstr "你也可以手动提供标志："

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:336
msgid "Object Methods"
msgstr "对象方法"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:338
msgid ""
"Object methods are registered by ``.method()``. Both non-virtual and "
"virtual methods are registered the same way."
msgstr ""
"对象方法通过 ``.method()`` 注册。非虚拟和虚拟方法都以相同的方式注册。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:341
msgid ""
"Static member functions of a class are actually global functions, so "
"those should be registered as :doc:`global functions and not as object "
"methods <global>`."
msgstr ""
"类的静态成员函数实际上是全局函数，"
"因此应注册为 :doc:`全局函数而非对象方法 <global>`。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:345
msgid "Member Function"
msgstr "成员函数"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:365
msgid "Extend Class Interface Without Changing Its Implementation"
msgstr "在不更改实现的情况下扩展类接口"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:368
msgid "Global Functions Taking an Object Parameter"
msgstr "接受对象参数的全局函数"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:370
msgid ""
"It is possible to register a global function that takes a pointer or a "
"reference to the object as a class method. This can be used to extend the"
" functionality of a class when accessed via AngelScript, without actually"
" changing the C++ implementation of the class."
msgstr ""
"可以将接受对象指针或引用的全局函数注册为类方法。"
"这可以在通过 AngelScript 访问时扩展类的功能，而无需实际更改类的 C++ 实现。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:386
msgid "Member Functions from a Helper Object"
msgstr "来自辅助对象的成员函数"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:388
msgid ""
"Similar to global functions taking an object parameter, member functions "
"taking an object parameter from a helper object can also be registered as"
" class methods."
msgstr ""
"类似于接受对象参数的全局函数，来自辅助对象的接受对象参数的成员函数也可以注册为类方法。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:409
msgid "The parameter for receiving object will be located by the following logic:"
msgstr "接收对象的参数将按以下逻辑定位："

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:411
msgid ""
"Check if the first/last parameter is a reference/pointer to the type "
"being registered."
msgstr ""
"检查第一个/最后一个参数是否为正在注册的类型的引用/指针。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:414
msgid ""
"This is designed to keep consistency with existing C++ paradigm, such as "
"how ``std::invoke`` deals with a member function pointer."
msgstr ""
"这旨在与现有的 C++ 范式保持一致，例如 ``std::invoke`` 如何处理成员函数指针。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:433
msgid "Function Receiving ``asIScriptGeneric*``"
msgstr "接收 ``asIScriptGeneric*`` 的函数"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:447
msgid ""
"Make sure the method declaration matches what the registered function "
"does with the ``asIScriptGeneric``!"
msgstr ""
"确保方法声明与注册函数对 ``asIScriptGeneric`` 的处理匹配！"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:450
msgid "Methods Using Composite Members"
msgstr "使用复合成员的方法"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:452
msgid ""
"If the application class that is being registered uses composition, then "
"it is possible to register the methods of the composite members without "
"wrapper functions."
msgstr ""
"如果正在注册的应用程序类使用了组合模式，则可以在没有包装函数的情况下注册复合成员的方法。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:479
msgid ""
"The usage of the ``composite`` helper is :ref:`different <generic-"
"composite>` when you want to create generic wrapper for composite methods"
msgstr ""
"当你想要为复合方法创建通用包装器时，``composite`` 辅助函数的用法是 :ref:`不同的 <generic-composite>`"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:482
msgid "Tips for Registering Methods"
msgstr "注册方法的提示"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:484
msgid "Registering Argument-Dependent Interfaces"
msgstr "注册参数相关接口"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:486
msgid ""
"The member functions you want to register may have default arguments. "
"Besides, some C++ libraries use the `argument-dependent lookup (ADL) "
"<https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/language/adl>`_ to extend their "
"interfaces."
msgstr ""
"你想要注册的成员函数可能有默认参数。"
"此外，一些 C++ 库使用 `argument-dependent lookup (ADL) "
"<https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/language/adl>`_ 来扩展其接口。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:489
msgid ""
"You need a wrapper function for this kind of interface. For convenience, "
"you can also register them by lambda expressions."
msgstr ""
"你需要为这种接口提供一个包装函数。为方便起见，你也可以通过 lambda 表达式注册它们。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:505
msgid "Overloaded Member Functions in C++"
msgstr "C++ 中的重载成员函数"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:507
msgid ""
"It will be ambiguous to take address of overloaded functions, you need to"
" use ``overload_cast`` with arguments to choose the function you want."
msgstr ""
"获取重载函数的地址会产生歧义，你需要使用带有参数的 ``overload_cast`` 来选择你想要的函数。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:528
msgid "Object Properties"
msgstr "对象属性"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:530
msgid ""
"Class member variables can be registered, so that they can be directly "
"accessed by the script without the need for any method calls."
msgstr ""
"类的成员变量可以注册，以便脚本可以直接访问它们，而无需任何方法调用。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:534
msgid "Ordinary Member Variables"
msgstr "普通成员变量"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:553
msgid "Composite Members"
msgstr "复合成员"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:555
msgid ""
"If the application class that is being registered uses composition, then "
"it is possible to register the properties of the composite members "
"without wrapper functions."
msgstr ""
"如果正在注册的应用程序类使用了组合模式，则可以在没有包装函数的情况下注册复合成员的属性。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:584
msgid "Registering Types with Similar Interfaces"
msgstr "注册具有相似接口的类型"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:586
msgid ""
"Sometimes you may want to reuse code for binding similar types. The "
"binding generators of classes provide ``.use`` for reusing a certain set "
"of registering code."
msgstr ""
"有时你可能希望重用绑定相似类型的代码。类的绑定生成器提供了 ``.use`` 来重用特定的注册代码集。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:589
msgid ""
"For example, if your reference classes all use ``addref`` and ``release``"
" for reference counting, you can create a helper to register those "
"behaviours."
msgstr ""
"例如，如果你的引用类都使用 ``addref`` 和 ``release`` 进行引用计数，你可以创建一个辅助函数来注册这些行为。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:618
msgid "Operator Overloads"
msgstr "运算符重载"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:620
msgid ""
"Operator overloads are registered by `special method names "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_script_class_ops.html>`_"
" in AngelScript. You can just register them like ordinary methods."
msgstr ""
"运算符重载通过 AngelScript 中的 `特殊方法名称 "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_script_class_ops.html>`_ 注册。"
"你可以像注册普通方法一样注册它们。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:623
msgid ""
"However, the tools introduced in this section may help you register "
"operators more easily."
msgstr ""
"然而，本节介绍的工具可以帮助你更轻松地注册运算符。"

