#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:649
msgid ""
"The operators with ``T&`` as return type will return reference to the "
"object being used, so multiple assignment can be chained."
msgstr ""
"返回类型为 ``T&`` 的运算符将返回正在使用的对象的引用，因此可以链式进行多次赋值。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:655
msgid ""
"This wrapper requires ``operator<=>`` returns ``std::weak_ordering`` at "
"least, i.e., **no** ``std::partial_ordering`` support. The result of "
"three-way comparison will be translated to an integral value recognized "
"by AngelScript."
msgstr ""
"此包装器要求 ``operator<=>`` 至少返回 ``std::weak_ordering``，"
"即**不支持** ``std::partial_ordering``。"
"三路比较的结果将被转换为 AngelScript 可识别的整数值。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:659
msgid ""
"If the type is registered as value type, there will be some additional "
"predefined helpers. These helpers will return result by value, so they "
"cannot be used by a reference class."
msgstr ""
"如果类型注册为值类型，还会有一些额外的预定义辅助函数。"
"这些辅助函数将按值返回结果，因此不能用于引用类。"

