#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:710
msgid "Type Conversion Operators"
msgstr "类型转换运算符"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:712
msgid ""
"The type conversion operators can be used to convert types without a "
"conversion constructor. `This official document "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_script_class_ops.html#doc_script_class_conv>`_"
" has explained the logic of type conversion in AngelScript"
msgstr ""
"类型转换运算符可用于在没有转换构造函数的情况下转换类型。"
"`官方文档 "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_script_class_ops.html#doc_script_class_conv>`_"
" 解释了 AngelScript 中类型转换的逻辑。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:724
msgid ""
"The generated conversion operators will use the expression "
"``static_cast<T>(val)`` internally."
msgstr ""
"生成的转换运算符将在内部使用表达式 ``static_cast<T>(val)``。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:735
msgid "More Complex Operators"
msgstr "更复杂的运算符"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:737
msgid ""
"If you want to register an operator overload whose signature is not "
"listed above, you can try the tools in the external header "
"``asbind20/operators.hpp``."
msgstr ""
"如果你想注册一个签名未在上述列表中列出的运算符重载，可以尝试外部头文件 ``asbind20/operators.hpp`` 中的工具。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:740
msgid ""
"The operator tools use ``_this`` or ``const_this`` as a placeholder, and "
"use ``param<T>`` for parameters."
msgstr ""
"运算符工具使用 ``_this`` 或 ``const_this`` 作为占位符，并使用 ``param<T>`` 表示参数。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:743
msgid ""
"If you want to specify the return type, you can use ``->return_<T>()``, "
"which is designed to simulate the trailing return type ``auto f() -> "
"Return`` since C++11."
msgstr ""
"如果你想指定返回类型，可以使用 ``->return_<T>()``，"
"它旨在模拟 C++11 以来的尾置返回类型 ``auto f() -> Return``。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:777
msgid ""
"In some libraries like the STL, the ``operator[]`` doesn't have a "
"boundary check. You still need a wrapper function with checks for "
"registering it. Otherwise bad script can directly crash your application,"
" instead of giving a clear error message."
msgstr ""
"在像 STL 这样的一些库中，``operator[]`` 没有边界检查。"
"你仍然需要一个带检查的包装函数来注册它。"
"否则，有问题的脚本会直接导致应用程序崩溃，而不是给出清晰的错误信息。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:781
msgid ""
"If the ``operator*`` doesn't return the type being registered, e.g., dot "
"product of a math vector which returns a scalar type, the predefined "
"helpers will fail to deal with this kind of operator overloads, but this "
"tool can be your best friend."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``operator*`` 不返回正在注册的类型，例如返回标量类型的数学向量的点积，"
"预定义的辅助函数将无法处理这种运算符重载，但这个工具可以成为你的得力助手。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:793
msgid ""
"If the type involves in the operator is neither the class type being "
"registered nor primitive types, you may need to manually pass the script "
"parameter declaration."
msgstr ""
"如果参与运算符的类型既不是正在注册的类类型也不是基本类型，你可能需要手动传递脚本参数声明。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:802
msgid ""
"With the power of this tool, you can even register the ``<iostream>`` to "
"AngelScript. Here is an example from the unit test of asbind20."
msgstr ""
"借助这个工具的强大功能，你甚至可以将 ``<iostream>`` 注册到 AngelScript。"
"这是来自 asbind20 单元测试的一个示例。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:826
msgid "Operators for ``foreach`` (Experimental)"
msgstr "``foreach`` 的运算符（实验性）"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:828
msgid ""
"AngelScript has introduced the ``foreach`` loop in version 2.38. Here is "
"a simple way to add support for a container-like type:"
msgstr ""
"AngelScript 在 2.38 版本中引入了 ``foreach`` 循环。"
"以下是为类似容器的类型添加支持的简单方法："

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:843
msgid ""
"If the name of your value type cannot be auto-generated, e.g. non-"
"primitive types, you can specify them manually."
msgstr ""
"如果你的值类型的名称无法自动生成，例如非基本类型，你可以手动指定它们。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:851
msgid "Member Aliases"
msgstr "成员别名"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:852
msgid "You can register a member ``funcdef``."
msgstr "你可以注册一个成员 ``funcdef``。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:854
msgid ""
"Here use the ``script_array`` from unit tests as an example. The same "
"logic also applies to other classes."
msgstr ""
"这里以单元测试中的 ``script_array`` 为例。相同的逻辑也适用于其他类。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:864
msgid ""
"Unlike the raw AngelScript interface, you don't need to add the class "
"name into the declaration of member ``funcdef`` for asbind20."
msgstr ""
"与原始的 AngelScript 接口不同，对于 asbind20，你不需要将类名添加到成员 ``funcdef`` 的声明中。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:868
msgid "Template Types"
msgstr "模板类型"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:870
msgid ""
"A template type in AngelScript works similarly to how templates work in "
"C++. The scripts will be able to instantiate different forms of the "
"template type by specifying which subtype that should be used. The "
"methods for the instance will then be adapted to this subtype, so that "
"the correct handling of parameters and return types will be applied."
msgstr ""
"AngelScript 中的模板类型的工作方式类似于 C++ 中模板的工作方式。"
"脚本将能够通过指定要使用的子类型来实例化模板类型的不同形式。"
"实例的方法将随后适应此子类型，以便应用正确的参数和返回类型处理。"

#: ../../doc/object_type.rst:875
msgid ""
"It is quite complex to implement a template class for AngelScript, so "
"they are described in a separate page."
msgstr ""
"为 AngelScript 实现模板类相当复杂，因此它们将在单独的页面中描述。"
